sequenceDiagram
  participant F as Frontend
  participant I as identity
  participant P as progress
  participant A as achievement
  participant M as monitoring

  F->>I: RegisterParent(email, firstName, lastName, password)
  I->>I: ParentAccount.create()
  I-->>I: AccountCreated

  F->>I: AddChild(parentId, Lenny, 8)
  I->>I: ParentAccount.addChild()
  I->>I: CareRelation.create(PARENTAL, ACTIVE, grantedBy=parentId)
  I-->>I: ChildProfileAdded(parentId, childId, Lenny)
  I-->>I: CareRelationEstablished(PARENTAL)

  I->>P: ChildProfileAdded
  P->>P: ProgressRecord.create(childRef)

  I->>A: ChildProfileAdded
  A->>A: Player.create(childId, xp=0, level=1)

  I->>M: CareRelationEstablished(parentId, childId, PARENTAL)
  M->>M: Dashboard.create(observer=parentId, observee=childId)
